{"tid":43500,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你個街 一用4px集運就仆街","createTime":"2016-12-17T14:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T22:23:58.000Z","uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"352a913f5e61245f39da0d7495f588ed566e27f0","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:13:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n上幾次用四方集運都幾好 通常都係兩日到<br />\n咁我21號就去韓國<br />\n諗住17號有得出庫寄啦<br />\n咁18 19 20 3日完整 仲要自取 應該得啦掛<br />\n<br />\n仆街<br />\n點知我16號晚 佢話我知七點前俾錢都要第二日先出庫<br />\n我話我份件真係好急 個客服就叫我拿拿林俾錢<br />\n然後幫我夜晚黑出庫<br />\n有份件下午四點左右簽左收 去到七點都未入庫<br />\n我都唔合併佢 諗住放棄依份件<br />\n<br />\n點知琴晚冇寄到 今朝又無寄<br />\n依家同我講話星期一朝早寄<br />\n你老味 點樣星期二就收到<br />\n<br />\n即刻打去屌7啲客服<br />\n今日同左五個客服講野 <br />\n我話唔使你哋幫我寄啦我自己返大陸問返你地攞返份件 又唔得 我話我額外再俾錢你特別幫我寄得唔得 又唔得<br />\n搞左成八個幾九個鐘<br />\n最後都係解決唔到件事 一定要星期一寄<br />\n<br />\n依家佢話星期一朝早寄<br />\n一到咗香港就打俾我叫我去佢個總倉攞<br />\n大家有無試過？<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪真係一朝早就出庫 第二日會到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da813a2cb960c08439c43b901229fb1423c8b54d","tid":43500,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱雙12, 係慢d啦"},{"pid":"f61ea71627c4a4cfcf2348c4a8eee552d0123203","tid":43500,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239b978d5414797053e97d9e64658dad132ecfd8","tid":43500,"uid":44,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"急你就咪撚用集運喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩又1212<br />\n星期六日不嬲都有限度服務架喇<br />\n唔撚洗放假咩<br />\n要快俾多幾十蚊叫賣家直寄香港喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f5a2db126f3e24769f4cd591935056d5e2558e","tid":43500,"uid":44,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1518c6a00f45be99426b7d128d7c825d610f17ed","tid":43500,"uid":9860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"月頭寄到香港，到今日貨都未到手<br />\n垃圾CS"},{"pid":"0b5d7869ec70e8eb6b4dbfe5d20bf5285b1881eb","tid":43500,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"趕時間用集運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde9b808b1faed87aa1eaaf738169b1dc995f9ab","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"屌 咁之前用過都係2日<br />\n撚知今次會食咁大舊屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605fd5d9e4f7ae8ae4c4a69e3485c65d7fd24eda","tid":43500,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"順豐都唔好得去邊<br />\n12月1號 集好 比錢<br />\n12月13 發貨 <br />\n12月16 先到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417bd7197e56658f14f10a6353d82cc76147831d","tid":43500,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"試過台灣寄過嚟用順豐，夜晚7點收件，第二日晏就5點鐘就寄到上屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1598e6b18975a8e618e52c2f5f6205e0f9bb6de0","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順豐都唔好得去邊<br />\n12月1號 集好 比錢<br />\n12月13 發貨 <br />\n12月16 先到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係用順豐奶撚過野<br />\n咁一路4px 都幾好 以為佢想爬頭 咪用佢<br />\n<br />\n但順豐好既係有香港電話 一定有人跟<br />\n我打4px長途 要講普通話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6165291236f733889411a49f5e23cc21d141fe60","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過台灣寄過嚟用順豐，夜晚7點收件，第二日晏就5點鐘就寄到上屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時順豐真係好快 但要慢起上黎真係慢到份件會唔知去左邊嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a41f3e87e4167b201b17e3e2b79696358c29ec","tid":43500,"uid":42385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"前幾日問過客服 <br />\n正常下夜晚七點前俾集運錢當日寄<br />\n星期五俾錢既星期一寄<br />\n<br />\n我星期四俾錢當晚出庫 <br />\n星期五 下午三點幾完成清關<br />\n今日兩點收到sms可以自提點拎"},{"pid":"8394752eea0086365fe8d30d7b879b9644a7efed","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日問過客服 <br />\n正常下夜晚七點前俾集運錢當日寄<br />\n星期五俾錢既星期一寄<br />\n<br />\n我星期四俾錢當晚出庫 <br />\n星期五 下午三點幾完成清關<br />\n今日兩點收到sms可以自提點拎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 但係點知佢星期五係咁煩! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028d2dbca08437e4b656e4dce08a5075809bef45","tid":43500,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>順豐都唔好得去邊<br />\n12月1號 集好 比錢<br />\n12月13 發貨 <br />\n12月16 先到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係用順豐奶撚過野<br />\n咁一路4px 都幾好 以為佢想爬頭 咪用佢<br />\n<br />\n但順豐好既係有香港電話 一定有人跟<br />\n我打4px長途 要講普通話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我日日屌哂佢全家都無用<br />\n一樣等左十幾日先發貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後有咩急野 直送算數"},{"pid":"7944ad8cd4b5bb6a21b2fb14884d1ec61444c013","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>順豐都唔好得去邊<br />\n12月1號 集好 比錢<br />\n12月13 發貨 <br />\n12月16 先到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係用順豐奶撚過野<br />\n咁一路4px 都幾好 以為佢想爬頭 咪用佢<br />\n<br />\n但順豐好既係有香港電話 一定有人跟<br />\n我打4px長途 要講普通話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我日日屌哂佢全家都無用<br />\n一樣等左十幾日先發貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後有咩急野 直送算數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身唔急架囉16寄 20到 巳經預多左<br />\n講真 深圳寄落黎要幾耐<br />\n就算唔好彩查車 都只係查一日半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac949284ae8faa999a5cf3cbdd6cc2c19fedbd4","tid":43500,"uid":11663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:11:09.000Z","msg":"自己無睇截單時間<br />\n咁都有得怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ef935fdb40370911126b92cc3da5ee242a30d6","tid":43500,"uid":410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"用官集已經on9左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次急既叫賣家順豐直送香港，都係比多三十到四十蚊<br />\n如果係官方禁運既就私集算啦"},{"pid":"31e0f653d07c7a8e3101ccf4827c268324ec9340","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T21:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己無睇截單時間<br />\n咁都有得怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係佢應承左我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要我話自己返上大陸拎都唔比我拎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ff7c01e6174ffece041ee10f91cbe51eee7abc","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T21:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用官集已經on9左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次急既叫賣家順豐直送香港，都係比多三十到四十蚊<br />\n如果係官方禁運既就私集算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n官集我覺得幾好架 個系統幾方便 又可以退埋貨<br />\n我有3份件嘛 有1份唔肯寄黎香港<br />\n咪索性3間都用集運囉⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"1b2774de5db55be844dedbf53ee5f8520ad367e7","tid":43500,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T21:15:13.000Z","msg":"用緊快郵寶 <br />\n今日晏晝5點截單 聽日中午有短訊俾你拎得<br />\n新張營業 有幾個自取點首重7蚊港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174653e6b35f365fbb0ff33f7f279dbb4ac0f9b6","tid":43500,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T21:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊快郵寶 <br />\n今日晏晝5點截單 聽日中午有短訊俾你拎得<br />\n新張營業 有幾個自取點首重7蚊港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭先家姐話佢用開嗰間 晚上8點半前比錢 第二日中午有得拎囉!<br />\n真係蠢左啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4d69252d187805a8938fcc49d5098087